title: Elbow Grease Bicarbonate Of Soda 500g
features: Multipurpose cleaner for all around the home
NATURAL DEODERISER, DEGREASER, PLUG HOLE FRESHENER, STAIN REMOVER
description: Product Description Elbow Grease Bicarbonate of Soda is a powerful multipurpose cleaner for all around the home. Made from 100% natural ingredients, the non-scratch formula produces amazing results from removal of stains, burnt food or grease. It's deoderising capabilities can be used as a natural way of freshening up carpets and upholstary without expensive cleaning machines. Elbow Grease Bicarbonate of Soda can be used in various ways when mixed with other products from the range. Try adding a couple of teaspoons down a stinky plug hole mixed with Elbow Grease Concentrated Vinegar and leave for 10 minutes, wash away with hot water for a fresh, smell free plug hole. Combing the same mixture of Elbow Grease Bicarbonate of Soda with Elbow Grease Concentrated Vinegar and water in a container can also be used as a powerful mildly abrasive multipurpose cleaner for stain removal around the home.
